{"tid":2449673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華為將向蘋果、三星收取5G專利費","createTime":"2021-03-17T00:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T12:00:43.000Z","uid":33307,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4020a7b7f6d3cf0e13277a1c8500cee2d5a092e5","tid":2449673,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:42:59.000Z","msg":"華為表示，將向蘋果（美︰AAPL）、三星等手機巨頭收取5G專利許可費，此舉有可能為華為創造可觀的收入來源。華為打算將專利費重新投入研發，以保持其在無線網絡中的領先地位。<br />\n<br />\n華為首席法務官宋柳平表示，將與蘋果及三星談判費率及潛在的交叉許可協議。華為承略收取的費率將低於高通、易利信、諾基亞等競爭對手。華為對遵循5G標準的每部手機專利許可費上限為2.5美元。<br />\n<br />\n華為又指，美國的制裁不應影響其與美國公司之間交叉許可的能力，因這些專利是公開可用的。<br />\n<br />\n高通早前對每部iPhone索取7.5美元專利費，蘋果認為並不公平，雙方因此發生激烈爭執。<br />\n<br />\n2019年至2021年期間，華為應收取的專利和許可費約為12億至13億美元，但未說明多少來自5G專利。"},{"pid":"80e17a4b9d59b054e16d08da16758492f549dc44","tid":2449673,"uid":33307,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:45:57.000Z","msg":"被動收入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59148d6db343c9bbf4178f6a78fe534e6ecd3c98","tid":2449673,"uid":321002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:47:25.000Z","msg":"冇錢買養豬飼料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7398f9ae48ec385cd9200f1ec939a037a3ee6213","tid":2449673,"uid":297997,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:50:47.000Z","msg":"台面就係收費<br />\n<br />\n實際係回佣"},{"pid":"b9154d45a04bec37f585c6204f13f077805e127e","tid":2449673,"uid":10340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T00:52:57.000Z","msg":"想問下佢收咩錢，蘋果同三星用華為5G receiver?"},{"pid":"5a69b3a794658aa8eb59ebbb5c5e3a6485e07244","tid":2449673,